com.robopupu.api.dependency

Annotation Type Provides


  • @Target(value={CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD,TYPE})
public @interface Provides
    Provides is used to annotate methods or constructors that provide dependencies for injection. Provides annotation can have one annotation parameter of type Class that declares the type of the provided dependency.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements
